Edward LeSaint https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edward_LeSaint 0 Edward LeSaint (December 13, 1870 – September 10, 1940) was an American stage and film actor and director whose career began in the silent era. He acted in over 300 films and directed more than 90. He was sometimes credited as Edward J. Le Saint.
